<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Café Sandwich Menu</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f1ea;
            color: #4e342e;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #6d4c41;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .menu-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #795548;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #6d4c41;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .menu-item {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .menu-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .menu-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #5d4037;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .menu-item p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .price {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #795548;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        Café Sandwich Menu
    </header>
    <div class="menu-container">
        <h2>Classic & Traditional Sandwiches</h2>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Grilled Cheese <span class="price">₹150</span></h3><p>Melted cheese between buttery toasted bread.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Club Sandwich <span class="price">₹200</span></h3><p>Turkey or chicken, bacon, lettuce, tomato, and mayo on toasted bread.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>BLT <span class="price">₹180</span></h3><p>Bacon, lettuce, and tomato on toasted bread with mayo.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Egg Salad Sandwich <span class="price">₹160</span></h3><p>Creamy egg salad served on soft bread.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Ham & Cheese <span class="price">₹170</span></h3><p>Slices of ham and cheese, sometimes grilled.</p></div>
        
        <h2>Healthy & Light Options</h2>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Avocado Toast Sandwich <span class="price">₹190</span></h3><p>Mashed avocado, tomatoes, and sprouts on whole-grain bread.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Turkey & Hummus Wrap <span class="price">₹210</span></h3><p>Sliced turkey, hummus, spinach, and cucumbers wrapped in a tortilla.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Caprese Sandwich <span class="price">₹200</span></h3><p>Fresh mozzarella, tomatoes, basil, and balsamic glaze on ciabatta.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Cucumber & Cream Cheese <span class="price">₹160</span></h3><p>Cucumbers and herbed cream cheese.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Veggie & Hummus <span class="price">₹170</span></h3><p>Bell peppers, carrots, cucumbers, and hummus in a pita.</p></div>
        
        <h2>Breakfast & Sweet Sandwiches</h2>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Peanut Butter & Banana <span class="price">₹140</span></h3><p>Peanut butter and sliced bananas on toast.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Nutella & Strawberry <span class="price">₹180</span></h3><p>Sweet Nutella with fresh strawberries in a soft roll.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Bacon, Egg & Cheese <span class="price">₹190</span></h3><p>Crispy bacon, eggs, and melted cheese.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>French Toast Sandwich <span class="price">₹200</span></h3><p>Cream cheese, jam, or ham and cheese between French toast slices.</p></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
